@startuml collaboration_diagram
!theme plain
title Cardiomegaly Detection System - Complete System Collaboration Diagram

' System Actors
object Reception
object "General Doctor" as GD
object "Specialist Doctor" as SD
object "X-ray Technician" as Tech
object Admin

' Core System Components
object "Patient System" as PS
object "X-ray System" as XRS
object "AI Engine" as AI
object "Notification Hub" as NH
object "Admin System" as AS
object Database
object "File Storage" as FS

' === PATIENT WORKFLOW ===
' 1. Patient Registration
Reception --> PS : 1: registerPatient()
PS --> Database : 2: storePatient()
PS --> NH : 3: notifyDoctors()

' 2. Patient Triage
NH --> GD : 4: newPatientAlert()
GD --> PS : 5: viewPatients()
GD --> PS : 6: referToSpecialist()
PS --> NH : 7: notifySpecialist()

' 3. X-ray Request
NH --> SD : 8: referralAlert()
SD --> XRS : 9: createXRayRequest()
XRS --> Database : 10: storeRequest()
XRS --> NH : 11: notifyTechnician()

' 4. X-ray Processing
NH --> Tech : 12: requestAlert()
Tech --> XRS : 13: uploadImage()
XRS --> FS : 14: storeImage()
XRS --> AI : 15: analyzeImage()
AI --> Database : 16: storePrediction()
AI --> NH : 17: notifyDoctor()

' 5. Results Review
NH --> SD : 18: resultReady()
SD --> XRS : 19: viewResults()
XRS --> Database : 20: queryResults()

' === ADMINISTRATIVE WORKFLOW ===
' 6. System Monitoring
Admin --> AS : 21: viewDashboard()
AS --> Database : 22: getMetrics()
AS --> Admin : 23: displayAnalytics()

' 7. User Management
Admin --> AS : 24: manageUsers()
AS --> Database : 25: updateUsers()

' 8. Edit Request Workflow
Reception --> PS : 26: requestEdit()
PS --> NH : 27: notifyAdmin()
NH --> Admin : 28: editAlert()
Admin --> AS : 29: reviewRequest()
AS --> PS : 30: approveEdit()
PS --> NH : 31: notifyReception()

' === DATA FLOWS ===
' Core Data Operations
Database <--> PS : Patient Data
Database <--> XRS : Request Data
Database <--> AI : Prediction Data
Database <--> AS : System Data
FS <--> XRS : Image Files
FS <--> AI : Model Files

' Notification Flows
NH --> Reception : Status Updates
NH --> GD : Patient Alerts
NH --> SD : Request & Result Alerts
NH --> Tech : Processing Alerts
NH --> Admin : System Alerts

' Key Process Annotations
note right of PS
  **Patient Management**
  - Registration (PAT#### IDs)
  - Status tracking
  - Referral workflow
  - Edit requests
end note

note right of XRS
  **X-ray Processing**
  - Request creation
  - Image upload (JPEG/PNG)
  - Status tracking
  - Result delivery
end note

note right of AI
  **AI Analysis**
  - Image validation
  - Cardiomegaly detection
  - Confidence scoring
  - Result storage
end note

note right of AS
  **Administration**
  - User management
  - System monitoring
  - Edit approvals
  - Analytics dashboard
end note

note right of NH
  **Notifications**
  - Role-based alerts
  - Event-driven messaging
  - Status updates
  - System communications
end note

' Workflow Annotations
note on link #1 : Auto-generated\nPatient ID
note on link #6 : Specialist\nReferral
note on link #9 : X-ray Order\nCreation
note on link #15 : AI Cardiomegaly\nDetection
note on link #23 : Real-time\nDashboard
note on link #29 : Edit Request\nApproval

@enduml